  "detailed_description": "Vast and beautiful HD forests await you in this virtual reality game!  Hunt animals (fallen aliens in disguise) with exploding arrows (cartoonish destruction) in a variety of levels covering over 3 square miles (7 square kilometers) with many animals and foliage.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHave you ever wanted to climb trees in VR while making your way through forests while hunting? Then this is the game for you!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayable on:<br />\r\n- oculus touch devices (oculusquest linked, metaquest2 /oculusquest2 linked, metaquestpro linked, oculus rift, oculusrifts), <br />\r\n- valve index, <br />\r\n- hp reverb g2 with valve index controllers,<br />\r\n- pico4 PCVR<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEach level varies in both size and content. Explore levels with a variety of different features per level, some including: climbable trees, climbable castles / urban cities / villages, oceans, snow, dynamic weather, day/night cycles, dense scenic forests and climbable forests, and more!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMost of the animals (aliens) are fairly stationary as to try to be more camouflaged, as such this game / experience is largely about exploring and finding animals in a casual virtual environment.",
  "about_the_game": "Vast and beautiful HD forests await you in this virtual reality game!  Hunt animals (fallen aliens in disguise) with exploding arrows (cartoonish destruction) in a variety of levels covering over 3 square miles (7 square kilometers) with many animals and foliage.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHave you ever wanted to climb trees in VR while making your way through forests while hunting? Then this is the game for you!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayable on:<br />\r\n- oculus touch devices (oculusquest linked, metaquest2 /oculusquest2 linked, metaquestpro linked, oculus rift, oculusrifts), <br />\r\n- valve index, <br />\r\n- hp reverb g2 with valve index controllers,<br />\r\n- pico4 PCVR<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEach level varies in both size and content. Explore levels with a variety of different features per level, some including: climbable trees, climbable castles / urban cities / villages, oceans, snow, dynamic weather, day/night cycles, dense scenic forests and climbable forests, and more!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMost of the animals (aliens) are fairly stationary as to try to be more camouflaged, as such this game / experience is largely about exploring and finding animals in a casual virtual environment.",
